This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and 3D scene reconstruction. It could also belong to Robotics (cs.RO) as it mentions autonomous navigation and military applications. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) are also possible sub-categories as they are often used in computer vision applications. Finally, Signal Processing (cs.SD) could be a relevant sub-category as the paper deals with processing thermal images.
